metadata.name: Season 0 1
metadata.description:
Enlighten yourselves > https://bfan.link/season-0-light-beings

"Each Season will have a different vibe and style of music, in an effort to streamline the creative output of Three Oscillators and give enough time and equal focus on producing music, playing gigs, teaching music production as a day job and taking breaks to focus on health. Seasons are being planned with a duration of a year in mind for each one, but it's still in development. While Season 0 is focused on experimental sound design, the yet-to-be-announced Season 1 will focus more on [redacted]"

"With a distinct, dreamlike sound that crosses genres without sticking to one for too long, Three Oscillators' music is a diverse mix of music styles inspired from water, space, science fiction and tranquility."
